fr.data.customer

Class Customer

  • java.lang.Object
    • fr.data.customer.Customer

  • public class Customer
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is the customer class. Its purpose is to create, store and modify the customers's data. Each customer have a name, first name, birthday, insurance, number of insurance and a list of its allergies. The user can either change the data, add data or see them.
    Version:
    2.0 26 Apr 2021
    Author:
    Max Labbe, Mathieu Way, Ophelie Foucault
